   =20
 =20
Here=E2=80=99s a guy who=E2=80=99s starting a private dining club where mem=
bership is a non-fungible token,=C2=A0 criticizing a different guy starting=
 a different private dining club where membership is a non-fungible token:L=
itwak maintains that Maxwell Tribeca will be a very different experience fr=
om Flyfish.=C2=A0=E2=80=9CGary [Vaynerchuk] raised $14 million, good for hi=
m, but he sold his memberships to the highest bidders. That club will likel=
y be 90% crypto dudes,=E2=80=9D says Litwak. =E2=80=9CHe=E2=80=99s demonstr=
ated the potential to raise capital. But it ignores why people care about a=
 place to belong. [At Flyfish Club] anyone who can afford it can buy in, an=
d then pretend it=E2=80=99s a community.=E2=80=9DYeah no=C2=A0that=C2=A0NFT=
 private club is 90% crypto dudes but=C2=A0my=C2=A0NFT private club is diff=
erent, we allow in only the rarest apes.=C2=A0
