scope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decorat=
ion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00000=
0; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">sold the credit ris=
k of its derivatives</a> to its managing directors=E2=80=99 bonus pool, and=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26626731.270615/a=
