yle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So you do a trade where Credit Suisse makes the oli=
garch yacht loans, for branding and relationship and business development p=
urposes, and as far as the oligarchs are concerned it is a leading, generou=
s, flexible, commercial provider of yacht loans. But then it sells the defa=
ult risk of the oligarch yacht loans to people who have a sense of humor ab=
out=C2=A0oligarch yacht loan risk, because bank regulators absolutely do no=
