anges to the network. If the price of those tokens rose, they=E2=80=99d mak=
e even more money, and set up even more hot spots.=C2=A0</p></blockquote><p=
 style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThis,=E2=80=9D writes Roose, =E2=80=9Ci=
