rojects by providing an incentive to get in on the ground floor.=E2=80=9D T=
he more people who join the project after you, the more money you make. Ord=
inarily a network benefits from network effects, and you should join a netw=
ork that a lot of people already use. But crypto networks benefit from =E2=
=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26626731.270=
