d-color: #ccc;">token=C2=A0effects</a>,=E2=80=9D and you should join a netw=
ork that a lot of people=C2=A0<em>will use in the future</em>. There is som=
e guesswork involved there of course, and some incentive=C2=A0for hype. (=
=E2=80=9CA cardinal rule of Helium=E2=80=99s 140,000-member Discord chat se=
rver is that you=E2=80=99re not allowed to discuss token prices,=E2=80=9D n=
